children.content: ROADMAP CIAM LMFR - STEP 3 - Authentication account events are now sent to Data Streaming Platform and no more to REFCLI

Authentication account event is published for "everyone" and documented within dev API portal. Architecture driver 3 & 6 are now, for both REFCLI & CIAM.
CIAM does not have to connect to REFLCLI anymoreand publish his events to Data Streaming Platform
